{"tid":2387766,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"偶像賺了的錢都如何管理？Red Velvet Wendy薪水竟全上交給父母!","createTime":"2021-01-30T14:43:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T15:01:35.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ca7c85ca6478dfa159e212959b970166dd8ec96c","tid":2387766,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T14:43:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2021/01/30/550_1559837_1612001942.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2021%2F01%2F30%2F550_1559837_1612001942.webp&h=6c72cf89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日，在音樂脫口秀《神秘的唱片店》中，組合Red Velvet的成員Wendy透露了對「理財」的熱情。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2021/01/30/550_1559835_1612002072.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2021%2F01%2F30%2F550_1559835_1612002072.webp&h=4158ee73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n29日，在JTBC播出的《神秘的唱片店》中，訂閱人數均超過100萬的南韓人氣經濟Youtuber舒卡、讀報男、申師任堂獲邀出演節目。<br />\n<br />\n在聊到理財方面的話題時，擔當主持人之一的Wendy被另一主持尹鍾信問到「20多歲的人對理財很感興趣嗎？」這個問題。<br />\n<br />\n對此，Wendy表示：「我還沒有(理財)，但是慢慢想來了解一下。我把我的東西都託付給父母了，因爲相信他們，我也想邊學邊做，只是擔心會危險。」<br />\n<br />\n據悉，在韓國當地，父母替已成年的子女管理金錢的狀況十分常見，因此，Wendy會將錢交給父母管理也並沒有讓韓國網友們感到驚訝。<br />\n<br />\n不過，在K-POP界中，也有不少小小年紀便因「善於理財」而非常有名的藝人，像是秀智、多順、Yura等等，在投資地產方面十分有心得，每月光是收房租就已經有一筆不菲的收入。<br />\n<br />\n另外，Wendy出道後首次擔任主MC的《神秘的唱片店》於每週五晚上9點在JTBC播出，想知道更多關於Wendy的小故事，記得多收看節目啦!"},{"pid":"e42c8e1d8b41682681a6c12c4b47c6dfcb5b1a30","tid":2387766,"uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T14:43:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/egFisaJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FegFisaJ.gif&h=5d6ec726&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e9e387b1d6e48cc61769be1c3a5a0e99ca2c7e0","tid":2387766,"uid":61251,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T14:44:41.000Z","msg":"老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcdd68da10dcf99647b000e2aed98a8860598c26","tid":2387766,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T14:54:34.000Z","msg":"@喪"},{"pid":"a7ec866ed59c8f21b2cc322b06b8097e7154d28b","tid":2387766,"uid":386678,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T15:01:35.000Z","msg":"弱智樣<br />\n比佢自己洗一陣就冇哂"}]}